&lt;li&gt;Strategic Sparring: Challenge the client and internal teams with &quot;Growth Invention&quot; ideas, moving beyond execution to strategic impact.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commercial Governance: Own the P&amp;amp;L, SOWs, and profitability for the Business Group.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
