&lt;li&gt;A confident, outgoing, and positive personality.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are a natural people person who builds chemistry instantly.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Challenger Mindset: You aren&#39;t afraid to have sensitive conversations or reset expectations when budgets or timings shift.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
