&lt;p&gt;We need great execs who can flex their skills and support across a variety of work, including, but not limited to biddable media planning &amp;amp; buying, organic content planning, content production and more! - &lt;em&gt;Don&#39;t worry, we don&#39;t expect you to have experience in all these areas, just perhaps a bit of knowledge, the most important thing for us is your drive and passion to learn!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
