&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;406&quot;&gt;Maintain accurate project financial data across Salesforce, DEPTApps, and Anaplan&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;489&quot;&gt;Support billing, project setup, WIP tracking, and month-end close activities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;567&quot;&gt;Ensure contracts and SOWs are properly stored and accessible for project setup&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;647&quot;&gt;Support forecasting inputs and financial reporting preparation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;711&quot;&gt;Identify and escalate data discrepancies or inconsistencies to Managers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
